The AALS Position
\par 
}
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
The Association of American Law Schools (\u8220\'3fAALS\u8221\'3f) is a non-profit association of law schools committed to improving the legal profession through legal education.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 It functions \u8220\'3fas the learned society for law teachers and is legal education\rquote s principal representative to the federal government and to other national higher education organizations and learned societies.\u8221\'3f American Association of Law Schools, 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
What is the AALS?
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 at http:// www.aals.org/about.html. In 1990, the AALS voted to include sexual orientation as a protected category in law school non-discrimination policies. (Rosenkranz Decl. \u182\'3f 10). Accordingly, all of the more than 160 member law schools of the AALS extended their non-discrimination policies to cover sexual orientation. (
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Id.
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
).
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Section 6\u8211\'3f4 of the By\u8211\'3fLaws of the AALS requires member schools to, among other things, provide \u8220\'3fstudents and graduates with equal opportunity to obtain employment, without discrimination or segregation\u8221\'3f on the basis of sexual orientation and other protected categories. (Rosenkranz Decl. \u182\'3f 10, Ex. 1). Schools must communicate to employers their \u8220\'3ffirm expectation\u8221\'3f 
}
{\b1 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
{\*\bkmkstart co_pp_sp_4637_281_1}{\*\bkmkend co_pp_sp_4637_281_1}
{\b1 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
