*283
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 offer specific guidance as to what the military requires of the law schools in order to be deemed compliant with the Solomon Amendment (Am. Compl. \u182\'3f 37; Rosenkranz Decl. \u182\'3f 22; Eskridge Decl. \u182\'3f\u182\'3f 39\u8211\'3f55), and replied simply by way of notification that the schools remained in default (Am.Compl.\u182\'3f\u182\'3f 7(m), 37).
\par 
}
}
}
