It is also evident that the Solomon Amendment furthers an important governmental interest. Pursuant to its constitutional grant of authority, Congress has imposed on the military an affirmative obligation to \u8220\'3fconduct intensive recruiting campaigns to obtain enlistments\u8221\'3f in the Armed Forces. 
}
