{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
. And as the Third Circuit has recognized, \u8220\'3fCongress considers access to college and university employment facilities by military recruiters to be a matter of paramount importance.\u8221\'3f 
