{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 trend the American Association of Law Schools (\u8220\'3fAALS\u8221\'3f) voted unanimously in 1990 to include sexual orientation as a protected category. As a result, virtually every law school now has a comprehensive policy like the following:
\par 
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li200 
