{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Id.
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 at H3863. He urged his colleagues to \u8220\'3fsend a message over the wall of the ivory tower of higher education\u8221\'3f that colleges\rquote  and universities\rquote  \u8220\'3fstarry-eyed idealism comes with a price. If they are too good\u8211\'3for too righteous\u8211\'3fto treat our Nation\rquote s military with the respect it deserves [,] then they may also be too good to receive the generous level of taxpayer dollars presently enjoyed by many institutions of higher education in America.\u8221\'3f 
