{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 FAIR argues that the Solomon Amendment forces law schools to propagate, accommodate, and subsidize the military\rquote s recruiting, and therefore implicates each of the three varieties of compelled speech cases.
\par 
}
}
