Nor is the exemption for schools that provide a \u8220\'3fdegree of access by military recruiters [that] is at least equal in quality and scope to that afforded to other employers,\u8221\'3f 
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=L&pubNum=1000547&cite=32CFRS216.4&originatingDoc=Ic2740c37541211d9b17ee4cdc604a702&refType=LQ&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.DocLink)" }{\fldrslt 
