}}}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
. And \u8220\'3fCongress considers access to [institutions of higher education] by military recruiters to be a matter of paramount importance\u8221\'3f and an \u8220\'3fintegral part\u8221\'3f of military recruiting efforts. 
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&serNum=1986140447&pubNum=350&originatingDoc=Ic2740c37541211d9b17ee4cdc604a702&refType=RP&fi=co_pp_sp_350_86&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.DocLink)#co_pp_sp_350_86" }{\fldrslt 
